{"tid":328439,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"葉國謙倡港人申請中國公民身份證","createTime":"2017-07-19T14:42:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-20T00:17:37.000Z","uid":42804,"like":2,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ccda9cfd07f19bfb056a9c114f2ace686b443e01","tid":328439,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T14:42:36.000Z","msg":"林鄭會見港區人大政協 葉國謙倡港人申請中國公民身份證<br />\n<br />\n約30名港區人大政協今日與特首林鄭月娥會面個半小時，就新一份施政報告提交意見。港區人大代表葉國謙說，席間有15人發言，關心議題包括國情教育、房屋、安老、航運、金融等。他本人提出三個問題，分別是在內地設安老城，最好是高鐵可直達的地方；第二是多培養港人公民意識，建議香港人都可申請中國公民身份證；第三是善用港珠澳大橋的優勢。<br />\n<br />\n他說，林鄭較關注有人提出的改變工廈用途建議，至於一地兩檢亦有提及，但沒有具體討論。他說，席間沒有討論DQ議員的事宜，但他認為如果有人做錯事，不應推卸責任，如在財委會拉布是不顧香港發展利益。其他出席的還包括人大常委范徐麗泰、人大代表楊耀忠、鄭耀棠及譚耀宗等。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170719&amp;guid=56976761&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170719%26guid%3D56976761%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&d=dG8WLkYDNMcC3X2tWQInyKNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=b825371c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170719%26guid%3D56976761%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&h=e38ce794\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170719&amp;guid=56976761&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"007ac089cc4753f3abd818dd2d50b0e4396ac17f","tid":328439,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T14:44:04.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"ea0fce76771426122857b65f46a3584941ab7fd5","tid":328439,"uid":49344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T14:45:39.000Z","msg":"申請澳洲pr 好過啦"},{"pid":"a4765243bf7055ac01ff82dccb0b1be7e6a9f013","tid":328439,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T14:49:57.000Z","msg":"有身份證等唔等於有戶籍？"},{"pid":"ef17e274d303d236cf48cf89ddd5badd874e40bb","tid":328439,"uid":7